{"tid":2015220,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【警暴聽證會！】邀請公眾人士出席聽日沙田區議會特別大會","createTime":"2020-05-13T13:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T03:49:46.000Z","uid":138409,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"37caaaddc4010f577b6ec0c389c330d5e22a0b48","tid":2015220,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T13:46:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"></span><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CommunityShaTin/photos/a.175290729734297/630417710888261/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCommunityShaTin%2Fphotos%2Fa.175290729734297%2F630417710888261%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=c0646a98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CommunityShaTin/photos/a.175290729734297/630417710888261/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xnPtGXW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxnPtGXW.jpg&h=e012b150&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沙田區議會明天將會召開特別大會，就五月一日警察進入沙田市中心新城市廣場驅趕市民的事件進行<span style=\"color: gold;\">公眾聽證</span>。<br />\n<br />\n沙田區議會現邀請曾經歷上述事件並有意發言的公眾人士，於<span style=\"color: gold;\">明天下午二時來沙田政府合署四樓</span>沙田區議會出席會議，以𨤳清事實，明辨真相。<br />\n<br />\n有意發言者請聯絡沙田區政聯絡人趙柱幫議員安排（電話：63471955）。<br />\n<br />\n沙田區政亦同時邀請各大傳媒到場採訪。如有查詢，歡迎與聯絡人趙柱幫議員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n沙田區議會特別會議的官方文件：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/st/doc/2020_2023/tc/dc_meetings_agenda/dc_poster_20_s2.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Fst%2Fdoc%2F2020_2023%2Ftc%2Fdc_meetings_agenda%2Fdc_poster_20_s2.pdf&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=611aca23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/st/doc/2020_2023/tc/dc_meetings_agenda/dc_poster_20_s2.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"ae11c48144477700b5f6f207d5256e8b4e16e231","tid":2015220,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi